description: You may pass your turn without playing a hero once during the laning phase.
\bigPush \bigPush \bigPush if \roam on one friendly hero in lane.
When played to lane, opponent must play to same lane on their next turn.
\warrior or \specialist Choose when this hero is played to lane.
\bigVision \bigVision \bigVision OR \bigRoam. Choose when this hero is played to lane.
\support or \assassin Choose when this hero is played to lane.
Most \roam. \vision and \push count as minus toward your \roam count.
Most \vision. \push and \roam count as minus toward your \vision count.
Most \push. \vision and \roam count as minus toward your \push count.
\bigVision \bigPush \bigRoam This hero's icons can only gain points via laning.
3 Lanes. First lane drawn is worth 2x points. \newline 1\vp per \push
3 Lanes. First lane drawn is worth 2x points. \newline 2\vp per \roam
When played to lane, you may swap two friendly heroes in play.
Double the icons on another hero in the same lane.
\specialist or \support Choose when this hero is played to lane.
\bigPush \bigRoam \bigRoam if only friendly hero in lane.
\assassin or \warrior Choose when this hero is played to lane.
When played to lane, choose a hero. Opponent must play that hero on their next turn.
\bigRoam \bigRoam if \push on one friendly hero in lane.
\bigPush \bigRoam if 2\vision on one friendly hero in lane.
